        public CoupledModelI composeAsAtomicHIOA(ModelDescriptionI[] models,
                                         java.lang.String newModelURI,
                                         SimulatorI simulationEngine,
                                         CoupledModelFactoryI cmFactory,
                                         java.util.Map<java.lang.Class<? extends EventI>,EventSink[]> imported,
                                         java.util.Map<java.lang.Class<? extends EventI>,ReexportedEvent> reexported,
                                         java.util.Map<EventSource,EventSink[]> connections,
                                         java.util.Map<StaticVariableDescriptor,VariableSink[]> importedVars,
                                         java.util.Map<VariableSource,StaticVariableDescriptor> reexportedVars,
                                         java.util.Map<VariableSource,VariableSink[]> bindings)
                                  throws java.lang.Exception
        compose the HIOA and return the resulting coupled HIOA that can be used as an atomic HIOA.

        Contract

         pre     models != null and models.length > 1
 pre     (forall i : models[i] != null)
 pre     newModelURI != null
 pre     cmFactory != null
 pre     imported != null
 pre     reexported != null
 pre     connections != null
 pre     importedVars != null
 pre     reexportedVars != null
 pre     bindings != null
 post    ret != null
        Parameters:
        models - models to be composed.
        newModelURI - URI of the resulting coupled model.
        simulationEngine - the simulation engine of the model.
        cmFactory - factory creating the right type of coupled model.
        imported - imported events and their conversion to submodels imported ones.
        reexported - exported events from the coupled model and their conversion from exported ones by submodels.
        connections - connections between exported and imported events among submodels.
        importedVars - variables imported by the coupled model that are consumed by submodels.
        reexportedVars - variables exported by submodels that are reexported by the coupled model.
        bindings - bindings between exported and imported variables among submodels.
        Returns:
        coupled HIOA resulting from the composition.
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - to do.
